Description: Techstep ASA is a Norway-based company delivering mobile technology that contributes to positive changes in working life and helps employees work more efficiently, safely and sustainably. Techstep ASA is the parent company of the Techstep Group, with business in Norway, Sweden and Denmark. The Group has four Segments, which are represented by the four geographic locations where the Group's entities are incorporated. Norway segment includes Techstep Norway AS, Mytos AS and Techstep Finance AS. Sweden segment include Techstep Sweden AB, Optidev AB and Techstep Finance AB. Denmark segment include Techstep Denmark ApS and Optidev ApS. Poland segment include Famoc S.A., Famoc Software Ltd. and Santa Maria Private Ventures sp. z.o.o.
